Sportsmail's Neil Ashton and Charles Sale heaped praise on Nathaniel Clyne and Wayne Rooney after England's 3-1 win against Scotland at Celtic Park.

Both Neil and Charles were delighted to see Rooney move a step closer to becoming England's all-time top scorer.

They also commented on the outstanding atmosphere at Celtic Park during the international friendly encounter.

 

